title "Cabal Street"
names {"cabal_1"}
descr
"The city here is much more quiet then around the lake.  this looks to have
been one of the first roads built in Nymgaard.  You can still here the crowds
to the north where Cabal street meets Papi Way.  Looking to the east
you see a walk way leading up to the city Hall and suddenly realize why this was
