"You have come to a peaceful part of town.  The walk is made of beautiful
white marble.  It shimmers almost like crystal.  Bushes have been lovingly
grown into an arch over the side walk.  You can here the sound of a bubbling
fountain to the east towards the City Hall and Cabal street is to the west."

