names {"walk_2"}
descr
"The white marble walk around the fountain and the soft bubbling sound give
this place a peaceful almost divine feeling.  Citizens sit on the many benches
around the fountain resting from there days labors and talking of the events
of the month.  This place is so quiet and peaceful you can even hear
birds chirping from trees near by.  You can sit and rest a while and meet
some of the Citizens or head east into the City hall.  The walk heads back
towards Cabal Street to the west."

