city_1
title "City Hall Foyer"
names {"city_1"}
descr
"As you stand in the foyer of Nymgaards City hall you suddenly realize how
much the gods must have helped in the building of this city.  The walls
are made of perfectly cut white marble bricks and sealed together buy a black
shiny mortar.  The floor is smooth as glass and is a royal blue color.
Even if this building was constructed by the best dwarven or gnome masons
they could have only completed it so perfectly with the gods divine help.
The foyer stretches off to the east into the building or you can head west
out towards the city."

