"You have entered the center Chamber of the Nymgaard City Hall.  The marble
brick of the walls shine in an almost blinding light and the high dome ceiling
seems to stretch up forever.  The blue glass like floor glows as you walk along
and marvel at the beauty of the building.  The Chamber of knowledge is
off to the north and the Chamber of Ideas is towards the south. A hall leads
east towards the offices of the city hall while the foyer heads out
to the west  A large spiral ivory stair case heads down into a darker part
of the building."

