title "Rest In Peace Chapel"
names {"rip chapel","chapel"}
descr
"The chapel is a small room with a number of dark brown wooden pews many
of them tear stained from the years of grief this place has seen.  There
is a private, curtained off section to one side for family members  of
the dearly departed. It is obvious this place has seen much sadness. A
large podium is positioned at the front of the chapel next to where the
casket stands for viewing. On tables around the room stand fresh flowers
replenished daily by the staff of the funeral home."

ALWAYS_LIGHT
movement SECT_INSIDE
flags {UNIT_FL_NO_WEATHER, UNIT_FL_INDOORS}

extra {"pew"}
