mort_cask
title "Rest In Peace Casket Room"
names {"rip casket room","casket room","casket"}
descr
"Although the staff at the funeral home have tried to take some of the
depressiveness out of this room you still get an eerie feeling walking
around in it, viewing all the caskets from the tiniest one about 3 feet
long to the very largest big enough to hold a mighty warrior. Each is
shown with its lid open showing a silk padded lining  inside. All the
caskets are made of the very best quality and  you notice signs around
the place urging you to plan ahead. The entrance is back to the west and
a flight of stairs can be seen leading downwards."

